==Description==

The '''TechDraw ExtensionIncreaseDecimal''' tool increases the number of decimal places of the dimension text.

==Usage==

# Select one or more dimensions.
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionIncreaseDecimal.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionIncreaseDecimal|Increase Decimal Places]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|TechDraw → Extensions: Dimensions → [[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionIncreaseDecimal.svg|16px]] Increase Decimal Places}} option from the menu.
# The number of decimal places of the selected dimensions is increased by one.

==Notes==

* The maximum number of decimal places is 9.


